```{r ampulla 33069083, include=FALSE}

PMID_33069083 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('33069083', database = 'PubMed')

citation_33069083 <- paste0(PMID_33069083$journal,' ', PMID_33069083$year, ' ', PMID_33069083$month,';', PMID_33069083$volume,'(', PMID_33069083$number,'):', PMID_33069083$pages)

PubMed_33069083 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_33069083$eprint)

doi_33069083 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_33069083$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
